==Korean==
三一 (literally, 3 1) is an abbreviation for "Samil" as in [[三]][[一]][[運動]] ([[Wikipedia:Samil movement]]). It refers to the third month and first day of the year (American date style: 3/1) in which mass demonstrations occurred in Korea beginning March 1, 1919.

